author: Ebony Bowden
title: Bachelorette Australia 2015: Take our quiz to find out which bachelor you are
text:
Take our quiz to find out which bachelorette you are Richie eliminated by Sam Frost ahead of finale It's the dating show that stops the nation. On Thursday night, Bachelorette Sam Frost will decide her forever guy as the country waits with bated breath.
But who will it be? Could you stand a chance at making it to the final two? Are you suave like soccer player Michael or romantic like rugged tradie Sasha?
Take our quiz to find out which of the bachelors you would be.
